<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor's Personal Info</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #0073e6;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .doctor-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .doctor-info img {
            max-width: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .doctor-details {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Doctor's Personal Information</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="doctor-info">
           <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/medical-concept-indian-beautiful-female-260nw-1635029716.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="doctor-details">
                <h2>Dr. Xyz, MD</h2>
                <p>Specialty: Cardiologist</p>
                <p>License Number: 12345</p>
                <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>
                <p>Email: xyz.doe@example.com</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>About Dr. Xyz</h2>
        <p>
            Dr. Xyz is a highly experienced cardiologist with a passion for helping patients maintain a healthy heart.
            He graduated from a prestigious medical school and has been practicing medicine for over 15 years. He is dedicated
            to providing the best care to his patients and is committed to ongoing research in the field of cardiology.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
